message.text:
Bencana24 truly begins now. Today we've started receiving information on bad flooding in both Kelantan and Terengganu. 

Our relief convoys will start deploying starting Friday on a scheduled basis. The field kitchen has been requested. We are now planning on sending #SantapanHeroMeals and critical dry goods only at this stage. 

Volunteers & vehicles needed. Able to deploy Friday - Sunday (29 Nov - 01 Dec). Destination Terengganu and Kelantan. Petrol, toll, accomodation and food provided. No other allowance. Must be fit and healthy. Expect for a minimum drive of at least 10 hours one way. 

Preferably 4WD. We have more requests than vehicles now. For safety purposes and because we most probably will go through some lightly flooded roads, a 4WD is preferred. 

Contact Azren Harun 0178835249 or William 0129488560.

Items we are accepting for donations are as follows:

1. Diapers (all sizes)
2. Sanitary Pads
3. Adult Diapers (all sizes)
4. Formula Milk (1-6 months, 1-3 years) any brand. 

Donations can be sent to Kembara Kitchen between Thursday (28 Nov) till Saturday (30 Nov), 9am - 5pm. We will inform if there's any extension of time for you to drop off your donations.

For those who wish to donate in cash for purchases, you can do so to

Acc Name: Kembara Kitchen
Acc Num: 8602542231
Bank Name: CIMB
REF: Bencana24
Email: yilynchan@sosprime.com

Thank you 

 #bencanaalam #Bencana #banjirmalaysia #volunteermalaysia #sukarelawanbanjir #retort #Malaysia #sukarelawan #sediadimakan #4wdmalaysia #banjirterengganu #banjirkelantan #mtl #monsuntimurlaut

Kami di Marlo & Friends Petshop mendoakan agar dipermudahkan segala urusan mangsa banjir di negeri-negeri terlibat. Moga tidak dilupakan juga kucing peliharaan serta haiwan gelandangan lain umumnya. Semoga banjir cepat surut & kehidupan dapat berjalan seperti biasa. Aamiin. 🤲🏻
